snippet.title: Charly Jordan - Trusting Your Gut
snippet.description:
Today we are joined by model, entrepreneur, DJ, and social media star, Charly Jordan. On this episode we dive into talking about being big on social media before there were social media platforms, how Los Angeles is a city that promotes competitive grinding, and authenticity versus fake connections. We also talk about navigating the DJ world as a woman, how having a large following can be different from being famous, and knowing when to trust your gut even if it means giving up an opportunity. 

“There’s a social hierarchy in society that imitates high school”
